## ğŸ§® FAIR+CARE Transformation Matrix

| FAIR Dim. | CARE Dim. | Property | Reference | Purpose |
|:------------|:-----------|:-----------|:------------|:-----------|
| **Findable** | Collective Benefit | `transform_manifest.json` | FAIR F1 | Provides lineage trace for transformations |
| **Accessible** | Responsibility | `cf_fix_logs.json` | FAIR A2 | Records metadata harmonization actions |
| **Interoperable** | Ethics | `reprojection_trace.log` | FAIR I3 | Ensures coordinate consistency across hazards |
| **Reusable** | Equity | `transform_checksums.json` | FAIR R1 | Guarantees reproducibility and verification |

